  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 7</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 21 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 9 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 22</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H, M, E</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You fire a large concentration of webbing from your mouth, creating a web at the target square, which is treated as a web spun by a Monstrous Spider one size larger than you (see D20 Modern, p245) and lasts for 1d4 hours or until destroyed. Any creature caught in a cone between you and the target square (its width reaches only up to 10 ft) must save or be pushed back into the web.<br><br>To properly use this technique, the target square must be capable of supporting a web.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 7 Chakra and 1 additional kumonosu to increase the size of the web by 10 x 10 ft (and thus widen the cone), up to a total of a 50 ft squares.</p>\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
